A RESOLUTION
1 Recognizing and commending the Henry County District Attorney's Victim Services Unit;
2 and for other purposes.
3 WHEREAS, the Henry County District Attorney's Victim Services Unit is dedicated to
4 providing compassionate and comprehensive support to victims of felony crime; and
5 WHEREAS, the unit consists of eight highly committed advocates, including two specialists
6 who focus on crimes against children and domestic violence cases; and
7 WHEREAS, these advocates assist victims in navigating the complexities of the legal
8 process, ensuring they receive the necessary guidance, resources, and emotional support to
9 pursue justice; and
10 WHEREAS, February 5, 2025, marks Stand With Survivors Day at the state capitol, a day
11 dedicated to raising awareness and advocating for the rights and safety of domestic violence
12 survivors; and
13 WHEREAS, it is abundantly fitting and proper that this remarkable unit be appropriately
14 honored during this special time.
