15 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES that
16 the members of this body recognize and commend the Henry County District Attorney's
17 Victim Services Unit for its dedicated, effective, and efficient service on behalf of those in
18 need as well as extend sincere best wishes for continued success.
